# Watchlist of TRACKS — one per line. Copy this file to `inputs/tracks.txt` and edit.
# Run:  lucidadl tracks
#
# Each line can be:
#   - a search "artist - title"        -> best Qobuz match is downloaded
#       Red Hot Chili Peppers - Otherside
#   - a direct track URL
#       https://play.qobuz.com/track/24107150
#   - a playlist/album URL             -> downloads all its tracks
#
# Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
# Already-downloaded items (tracked in the state file) are skipped.

Red Hot Chili Peppers - Otherside
